usage() {
  cat <<'USAGE'
Usage:
  ./tools/dashboard-data [json]
  ./tools/dashboard-data live-status

Print a read-only JSON snapshot for the dashboard control-center data layer.
The live-status subcommand prints the small, fast-changing status payload used by the overview cards.
USAGE
}

